WEBVTT

00:06:59.117 --> 00:07:02.085
he's been focused
on being accountable for that act

00:07:02.109 --> 00:07:04.959
and doing his best to make amends
from behind bars.

00:07:06.458 --> 00:07:12.379
He brought that work into a design
for a community center

00:07:12.403 --> 00:07:14.536
for reconciliation and wellness.

